Bullet Point 1: 12 bolt fill valve with check valve flapper
Bullet Point 2: 2 1/4 inch OD fill tube and twist lock cap
Bullet Point 3: Bolted in plastic flapper for rollover protection
Bullet Point 5: Used on fuel cells with or without safety foam installed
Description 1: This 12 bolt fill valve with check valve flapper can be retrofitted to bolt onto any of our standard 12 hole pattern cap assemblies.  It has a 2 1/4 inch OD fill tube and twist lock cap.  It features a bolted in plastic flapper for rollover protection and comes standard with an AN-10 tip over valve vent fitting.  Designed to be used on fuel cells with or without safety foam installed.  This is IMCA approved, made to reduce the cost for customers who require rollover protection, but do not want the extra cost of a spring loaded flapper.  Fuel cells built with this new filler installed will also come with a bat wing attached to the pickup hose to prevent the hose from curling or moving.
